## 3. Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "UI Layer"
        Main["main.dart<br/>(MyApp, MainScreen)"]
        Auth["Auth Screens<br/>(WelcomePage, SignInPage, RegisterPage, LoginScreen)"]
        Dash["DashboardScreen"]
        Sched["ScheduleScreen"]
        Notif["NotificationsScreen"]
        Prof["ProfileScreen"]
        SCR["ScheduleChangeRequestScreen"]
        CPW["ChangePasswordScreen"]
        EP["EditProfileScreen"]
    end

    subgraph "State Layer (Riverpod)"
        AP["authProvider"]
        DP["dashboardProvider"]
        SP["scheduleProvider"]
        NP["notificationProvider"]
        CNP["classNotificationProvider"]
        API_P["apiServiceProvider"]
    end

    subgraph "Service Layer"
        API["ApiService"]
        SS["SecureStorageService"]
        CNS["ClassNotificationService"]
    end

    subgraph "Models"
        UM["UserProfile / User"]
        DM["DashboardData"]
        SM["ScheduleResponse"]
        NM["NotificationItem"]
        CM["ConflictModel"]
        SCRM["ScheduleChangeRequest"]
    end

    Main --> AP
    Main --> Auth
    Main --> Dash
    Dash --> DP
    Sched --> SP
    Notif --> NP
    Prof --> AP
    SCR --> API_P

    AP --> API
    DP --> API
    SP --> API
    NP --> API
    API --> SS
    CNP --> CNS
```

