## 7. Screen Navigation Flow

```mermaid
graph LR
    Splash["AppOpeningLoadingScreen"] --> AuthCheck{Authenticated?}
    AuthCheck -->|No| Welcome["WelcomePage"]
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| MainScreen
    Welcome --> SignIn["SignInPage"]
    Welcome --> Register["RegisterPage"]
    SignIn -->|Success| MainScreen
    Register -->|Success| MainScreen

    MainScreen --> Dashboard["DashboardScreen"]
    MainScreen --> Schedule["ScheduleScreen"]
    MainScreen --> Notifications["NotificationsScreen"]
    MainScreen --> Profile["ProfileScreen"]

    Profile --> EditProfile["EditProfileScreen"]
    Profile --> ChangePassword["ChangePasswordScreen"]
    Schedule --> SCR["ScheduleChangeRequestScreen"]

    MainScreen -.->|"Profile incomplete"| CompletionDialog["FacultyProfileCompletionDialog"]
```

