## 8. API Endpoints Used

Based on code references across all providers and screens:

| Endpoint | Method | Used By |
|---|---|---|
| `/auth/login` | POST | `authProvider` |
| `/auth/register` | POST | `authProvider` |
| `/faculty/profile` | GET | `authProvider` |
| `/faculty/profile` | PUT | `editProfileScreen`, `profileCompletionDialog` |
| `/faculty/dashboard` | GET | `dashboardProvider` |
| `/faculty/schedule` | GET | `scheduleProvider` |
| `/faculty/schedule/weekly` | GET | `weeklyScheduleProvider` |
| `/faculty/notifications` | GET | `notificationsProvider` |
