## 9. Theme System Summary

The primary design system in [app/configs/theme.dart](file:///c:/Users/HVergara/scheduling_mobile/lib/app/configs/theme.dart):

- **Font:** Outfit (bundled in `assets/fonts/`)
- **Primary:** `#465FFF` (vibrant blue)
- **Card gradient:** `#1D4ED8` → `#465FFF`
- **Background:** `#F4F7FC` (light blueish gray)
- **Text primary:** `#111827` / Secondary: `#667085`
- **Both light and dark themes** defined (dark theme not exposed to user)
- **Material 3** enabled
- Consistent `AppSpacing`, `AppRadius`, `AppMotion` design tokens

